popularityCurve.label: i thought i saw how stories of this kind could steal past certain inhibitions which had paralyzed much of my own religion in childhood but supposing that by casting all these things into an imaginary world stripping them of their stained-glass and sunday school associations one could make them for the first time appear in their real potency could one not thus steal past those watchful dragons
